title: The Ghost in the Underblows by Alfred Young Fisher
description:
Pages 198-199. 
Left: 2 sections of poetry in black text 18 lines each. 198 inscribed in lower left corner. 
Right: Abstract design with 4 figures in black, white and red. 3 black vertical ovals with smaller red and white ovals inside as well as black and white details at left. Red rectangles extend from below center of oval. To right: 1 black vertical rectangle bisecting 5 red circles. All 4 figures equal in height. In background: horizontal rectangle consisting of thin black lines behind center of 4 figures. Lines extend down past left of figures to form a vertical rectangle.
name: Book
